messages.speech:
You can have an hour and a half of peer tutoring a week for each class that you are taking during each semester. You are encouraged to stop in and sign up for an appointment, but walk-in appointments are welcome. Other support centers see students on a walk-in basis. There is no limit on the number of hours you can spend in any of the support centers.
http://www.century.edu/support-services/academic-resource-centers
